    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it feels like a lot of the talk lately is about how these companies are basically 'unavoidable' platforms. do you think the current antitrust framework is actually equipped to handle them, or is the whole system basically outdated at this point?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
